# 301 redirect map for the Odoo → Astro migration.
# Format: Netlify / Cloudflare Pages `_redirects`. The trailing `301!` forces
# the redirect even if a file exists. Adjust paths to the EXACT old Odoo URLs
# (verify in Google Search Console > Pages and your old sitemap).
#
# LAUNCH BLOCKER: without these, the ranking + backlink equity of the old URLs
# is lost. Confirm every currently-indexed Odoo URL has a line here.

# ---- Canonical host: keep www (the host Odoo ranks on), 301 the apex ----
